How to Build for Android
------------------------

Prerequisites:

1. Android Studio >= 3.2.1

2. latest Android SDK

3. latest Android NDK

To build:

1. Create 'gradle.properties' file in Gradle user home directory (which defaults to $USER_HOME/.gradle)
containing signing configs:
    RELEASE_STORE_FILE=<path to the store file>
    RELEASE_STORE_PASSWORD=<store password>
    RELEASE_KEY_ALIAS=<key alias>
    RELEASE_KEY_PASSWORD=<key password>

2. Import project to the Android Studio

3. Use the Build menu to build project
